This section describes how to launch a new virtual machine from the
imported Gluster Virtual Storage Appliance Template.

*To quickly launch a new virtual machine from the imported Gluster
Virtual Storage Appliance Template*

1.  Using XenCenter, right-click the Gluster Virtual Storage Appliance
Template and select *Instant VM from Template*.

A new virtual machine is added and started. The new virtual machine will
be listed in the XenCenter inventory.

*Note:* You can right-click the Gluster Virtual Storage Appliance
Template and select *New VM from Template* to add a new VM and customize
it.

